snippet.title: Sex Chess Gameplay No Commentary an Adult Chess Game
snippet.description:
It is said that the Satan is the rightful Ruler of Hell, but even here he will have to fend off the annoying "forces of Good with BIG swords" that want to free all of the sinners from his underground dungeon.
Take on the role of a hellish BDSM practitioner, the Devil's most important henchman, and crush the leader of the Light Forces in a six round duel on the chessboard. 
Use your intellect and cunning to show the brazen liberators their place.​
